creator: Ready Education
descriptionHtml:
The Palmer College app brings your campus to your fingertips and connects you with classmates and friends. Access events, calendars, clubs, maps and more! Stay organized, connect with classmates and improve your study habits.

Features that help with student life:
+ Events: Find events on campus.
+ Campus Services: Learn about services offered.
+ Groups & Clubs: Get involved with clubs, groups and professional organizations.
+ Campus Feed: Join the campus discussion.
+ Students List: Connect with fellow students.
+ Classes: Manage classes, create to-dos and reminders, and stay on top of assignments.
+ Campus Map: Directions to classes, events and offices.
+ Tour: Explore the campus
descriptionShort: Official app for Palmer College of Chiropractic

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We improve the app for our users with bi-weekly updates to add new features, squash bugs and improve app performance. We'd love to hear from you if you have any feedback for us.
